{"_id":"5ilpPsUueWFrpNZR","name":"Flank (Menacing & Outflank)","type":"buff","img":"systems/pf1/icons/feats/two-weapon-fighting.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>When making a melee attack, you get a +2 flanking bonus if your opponent is threatened by another enemy character or creature on its opposite border or opposite corner.</p>\n<p>When in doubt about whether two characters flank an opponent in the middle, trace an imaginary line between the two attackers&rsquo; centers. If the line passes through opposite borders of the opponent&rsquo;s space (including corners of those borders), then the opponent is flanked.</p>\n<p>Exception: If a flanker takes up more than 1 square, it gets the flanking bonus if any square it occupies counts for flanking.</p>\n<p>Only a creature or character that threatens the defender can help an attacker get a flanking bonus.</p>\n<p>Creatures with a reach of 0 feet can&rsquo;t flank an opponent.<br /><br /></p>\n<p>Menacing</p>\n<p>This special ability can only be placed on melee weapons. A menacing weapon helps allies deal with flanked foes. When the wielder is adjacent to a creature that is being flanked by an ally, the flanking bonus on attack rolls for all flanking allies increases by +2. This ability works even if the wielder is not one of the characters flanking the creature.<br /><br /></p>\n<p><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\">Outflank</strong></p>\n<p><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\">You look for every edge when flanking an enemy.</em><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\" /><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\" /><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\">Prerequisites</strong><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\" /><span style=\"color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\">Base attack bonus +4.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\" /><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\" /><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\">Benefits</strong><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\" /><span style=\"color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\">Whenever you and an ally who also has this feat are flanking the same creature, your flanking bonus on attack rolls increases to +4. In addition, whenever you score a critical hit against the flanked creature, it provokes an attack of opportunity from your ally.</span></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"changes":[{"_id":"c8wkzbhz","formula":"6","operator":"add","target":"attack","subTarget":"mattack","modifier":"untyped","priority":0,"value":0}],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[]},"tag":"flankMenacingOutflank","useCustomTag":false,"flags":{"boolean":[],"dictionary":[]},"scriptCalls":[],"buffType":"temp","active":false,"level":"","duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"hideFromToken":false,"damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0},"range":{"maxIncrements":1}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"HJCc6PbpWWHpTj44":3},"flags":{}}
